      <title>西班牙通胀加速，支持欧洲央行逐步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙通胀率本月升幅超出预期，受基数效应影响，通胀率连续第二个月维持在 2% 以上，这为逐步降息提供了依据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国调查最严重空难：目前所知情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/south-korea-s-plane-crash-what-to-know-about-the-boeing-jet-bird-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此次空难造成 179 人死亡，两人幸存，是韩国最严重的商业航空事故。当局已取回两个黑匣子，即飞行记录器，预计它们将为他们提供有关飞机在韩国南部地区机场停机坪降落时爆炸前最后时刻的关键信息。调查重点是起落架故障和鸟击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/south-korea-s-plane-crash-what-to-know-about-the-boeing-jet-bird-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 07:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比波动率飙升，印度储备银行的货币策略成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/rupee-volatility-surge-puts-rbi-s-currency-strategy-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美元走强，人们越来越猜测印度央行可能会放松对印度卢比的严格控制，印度卢比波动率的指标跃升至一年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/rupee-volatility-surge-puts-rbi-s-currency-strategy-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 06:42:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦邀请电力存储投标以缓解供电危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/zimbabwe-invites-power-storage-bids-to-ease-supply-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦电力传输公司已邀请企业投标安装储能装置，作为缓解严重能源短缺问题的措施之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/zimbabwe-invites-power-storage-bids-to-ease-supply-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 06:10:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳赫勒：2025 年石油的最大变数是地缘政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/nakhle-geopolitics-biggest-wildcard-for-oil-in-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员关注 2025 年的风险，包括供应充足和特朗普政府的不可预测性，油价已趋于稳定。Crystol Energy 首席执行官 Carole Nakhle 在接受彭博社关于中东和非洲视野的 Christine Burke 采访时表示，地缘政治将成为影响油价的最大因素。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/nakhle-geopolitics-biggest-wildcard-for-oil-in-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 05:15:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日产汽车股价因本田交易疑虑而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/nissan-shares-slide-for-second-day-as-investors-take-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司股价下跌，两天内跌幅达 13%，原因是投资者担心该汽车制造商与本田汽车公司计划达成的交易条款将降低投资者在拟议的联合控股公司的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/nissan-shares-slide-for-second-day-as-investors-take-profit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 04:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金上涨 27%，在金属市场涨跌互现的一年中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金价格有望实现本世纪最大的年度涨幅之一，受美国货币宽松政策、持续的地缘政治风险以及各国央行的购买浪潮推动，黄金价格已上涨 27%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 04:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推动的比特币涨势在年底失去动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/bitcoin-btc-rally-fueled-by-trump-loses-steam-as-year-draws-to-close</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2024 年接近尾声，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 11 月初获胜所引发的比特币涨势正在停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/bitcoin-btc-rally-fueled-by-trump-loses-steam-as-year-draws-to-close</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 00:17:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者关注 2025 年前景，油价在清淡交投中保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价保持稳定，因交易员关注 2025 年的风险，包括充足的供应以及新一届特朗普政府的不可预测性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Dec 2024 23:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：投资者在年底前削减风险，股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-29/asian-stocks-poised-for-weak-open-after-us-losses-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于年底的不确定性，投资者削减仓位，亚洲股市下跌，美国和欧洲股票期货小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-29/asian-stocks-poised-for-weak-open-after-us-losses-markets-wrap</guid>
